data.description: Welcome to 135 Brazos. This like new home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a large flex room, and is situated on a spacious lot. The charming family room features a gas fireplace and seamlessly connects to the kitchen making it an entertainer's dream. Throughout the house you will find upgraded light fixtures and wall treatments. The above ground pool is in working condition.
